      <scopecontent id="aspace_fa33d33e3b36f920ecc3ba40edc550e9">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of faculty and personnel files, minutes, budgets, chronological files, and reports documenting the activities and operations of the Yale Department of Anthropology.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
